* Upgrade to Minetest@5.5.1
* Many improvements and bugfixes
* Major improvements to the Quiz Player Challenge mod:
  * ğŸ†•ï¸ï¸ New four arithmetic operation answer type (type): `calc`
  * ğŸ†•ï¸ï¸ Text type answers now support [Lua character pattern matching](https://www.lua.org/pil/20.2.html), if the answer is `pattern matching` string, then the answer must use two `/` wrapped.

